    {
      "id": "YwLKRjjepylDoRueRd1Fm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 549.6666666666663,
      "y": 2227.2619047619046,
      "width": 648.1993408203125,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "az",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 569116463,
      "version": 647,
      "versionNonce": 1886311571,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773484451785,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Prefix of the long url (bad idea)\n2. Random number generator 10^9 which is at least  10 characters long\n    - base62 encoding, 0-9, A-Z, a-z\n    - 62^6 = 56B\n    - Birthday Paradox\n    - 880k collisions out of 1B\n    - We just need to check for collision first\n3. Hash the long url\n    - md5(longUrl) -> hash -> base62(hash)[:6]\n    -  same as above like 880k collission out of 1B\n4. COunter\n    - incrementing a counter ->  base62\n    - predictability  which is bad for security\n        -\"waring,don't shorten private  urls\" (not possible)\n        - rate limiting\n    - bijective function\n        - sqids.org\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Prefix of the long url (bad idea)\n2. Random number generator 10^9 which is at least  10 characters long\n    - base62 encoding, 0-9, A-Z, a-z\n    - 62^6 = 56B\n    - Birthday Paradox\n    - 880k collisions out of 1B\n    - We just need to check for collision first\n3. Hash the long url\n    - md5(longUrl) -> hash -> base62(hash)[:6]\n    -  same as above like 880k collission out of 1B\n4. COunter\n    - incrementing a counter ->  base62\n    - predictability  which is bad for security\n        -\"waring,don't shorten private  urls\" (not possible)\n        - rate limiting\n    - bijective function\n        - sqids.org\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
