      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "File  Metadata:\n- fileId\n- folderId\n- file Name\n- Mime Type\n- Size\n- Compression Algo\n- Owner Id\n- Creation Timestamp\n-  Update Timestamp\n- S3Link\n- status: 'started'\n-  chunks: [\n    {\n        id as fingerprint,\n        status,\n        s3Link\n    }\n]\n- ... metadata",
