      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773668865491,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Upload large files: 50gb\n50gb @100mbps = 1hr 12 min\nChunk files on client to 5mb chunk\nFingerprint each chunk: hash(bytes)\n\n1. Chunk files on client to 5mb chunk\n2. Fingerprint each chunk: hash(bytes)\n3. Get pre-signed url\n4. Upload directly to S3\n5.update chunk metadata with completed status",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Upload large files: 50gb\n50gb @100mbps = 1hr 12 min\nChunk files on client to 5mb chunk\nFingerprint each chunk: hash(bytes)\n\n1. Chunk files on client to 5mb chunk\n2. Fingerprint each chunk: hash(bytes)\n3. Get pre-signed url\n4. Upload directly to S3\n5.update chunk metadata with completed status",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
