      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773669645919,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Deep Dive on Sync\n1. Sync to be fast\n- adaptive polling\n- delta sync to only detch\n    changed chunks\n\n2. Sync to be consistent\n- polling the DB\nOR event bus w/ cursor\n- Reconciliation",
